Boil a full #kettle{}.

Meanwhile, heat a drizzle of @oil{drizzle} in a #frying pan{} on medium-high heat.

Once hot, fry the @Diced British Chicken Thigh{240%g}, ~{8-10%minutes}.

Season with @salt{pinch} and @pepper{pinch}.

> IMPORTANT: Wash hands and utensils after handling raw meat. Cook so there's no pink in the middle.

Meanwhile, trim and halve the @Green Beans{150%g}.

Next, pour the boiled water into a #saucepan{} with @salt{1/2%tsp} on high heat.

Boil the @Egg Noodle Nest{2} and green beans, ~{4%minutes}.

Once cooked, drain and run under cold water.

When the chicken is cooked, stir in the @Bulgogi Sauce{100%g}, @Soy Sauce{25%ml}, @Sriracha Sauce{15%g} and @Water{50%ml} (see pantry).

Simmer, ~{1-2%minutes}.

Mix in the cooked noodles and beans. Add another splash of water if needed.

Share the noodles between your #bowls{}.

Sprinkle over the @Roasted White Sesame Seeds{5%g}.